autonumber

actor "User" as user
participant "HomeScreen" as UI
participant "CategoryActions" as CatActions
participant "ReminderActions" as RemActions
participant "CategoryReducer" as CatReducer
participant "ReminderReducer" as RemReducer

user -> UI: Selects category

UI -> CatActions: setActiveCategory(categoryId)
CatActions -> CatReducer: update activeCategoryId
CatReducer --> UI: updated state

UI -> RemActions: filterRemindersByCategory(categoryId)
RemActions -> RemReducer: apply category filter
RemReducer --> UI: updated reminders state

UI --> user: Displays only filtered reminders

@enduml
